Pod-Trac version 0.0.1

Convert a POD to trac wiki syntax, and create or update a page on a Trac wiki
with the current documentation of the module.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

Test::More
version
Test::Perl::Critic
File::Util
URI::Escape
File::Temp
HTTP::Request::Common
LWP::UserAgent
HTTP::Cookies
Pod::Simple::Wiki
Class::Accessor::Fast


